net.sf.mmm.util.query.api.feature

Interface FeatureSet<SELF extends FeatureSet<SELF>>

  • Type Parameters:
    SELF - the generic type of this query itself (this) for fluent API calls.
    All Superinterfaces:
    StatementFeature
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    InsertStatement<E,SELF>, JpqlUpdateStatement<E>, OrientDbInsertStatement<E>, OrientDbUpdateStatement<E>, StoreStatement<E,SELF>, UpdateStatement<E,SELF>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractInsertStatement, AbstractStoreStatement, AbstractUpdateStatement, FeatureSetImpl, JpqlUpdateStatementImpl, OrientDbInsertStatementImpl, OrientDbUpdateStatementImpl

    public interface FeatureSet<SELF extends FeatureSet<SELF>>
extends StatementFeature
    StatementFeature for a Statement allowing a SET clause.
